Package com.example.zhaorui.dvdcollector.Model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MyObserver
    The MyObserver is a observer to make sure everything updates in the interface on time.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cache
    The Cache is a temperate storage that allowed other functions to use without read and load to local file.
    Configuration
    The Configuration manages the config information of the app.
    ContextUtil
    The ContextUtil controls the content for loading from and writing to local files.
    DVD
    The DVD class manages information for DVD it provide function to set information for a DVD and get information from a DVD.
    Friend
    The Friend manage the selected friend's information of the current user.
    Friends
    The Friends class manages observers to make sure the friend list can be update on time on user's interface.
    Gallery
    The Gallery class manages photos that are used in this app.
    Internet
    The Internet class manages the internet connection of the app.
    Inventory
    The Inventory manages the inventory list for the current user it provide functions to add, delete and edit dvds.
    Search
    The Search class allowed users to search an inventory by name, category and sharable.
    SimulatedDatabase
    The Cache is a local database to store friend information.
